    public interface Instance
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.ChildOf<Service>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Augmentable<Instance>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Identifiable<InstanceKey>

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module config
    (Source path: META-INF/yang/config.yang): 

     list instance {
     key "name"
     leaf name {
         type string;
     }
     leaf provider {
         type leafref;
     }
 }
    The schema path to identify an instance is config/services/service/instance

    To create instances of this class use InstanceBuilder.
